{"tid":2435943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新任廣播處長稱我最著重黃藍，DQ《香港故事》並疑向《鏗鏘集》埋手","createTime":"2021-03-06T16:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T23:18:56.000Z","uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8921bc888c88eecb3c5480b79eb59ba37a293752","tid":2435943,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T16:24:42.000Z","msg":"戴住有色眼鏡，再同大家講何謂「持平」🥰<br />\n// #零傳媒經驗的廣播處長李百全 周四（4日）編輯會議上批評《香港故事》訪問樂隊LMF「唔decent（正經）」後。《蘋果》獲悉，李事後疑沒有看過該集的訪問，已決定抽起該集，同節目即將播出探討讀書文化等集數，李也沒有看過就決定抽起。據了解，當日李更在會上表明自己：「最著重黃藍」。//<br />\n<br />\n#清算港台<br />\n【李百全表明「最著重黃藍」 DQ《香港故事》包括LMF訪問 疑向《鏗鏘集》埋手】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3rn0MZt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3rn0MZt&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=ff2d67be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3rn0MZt</a><br />\n============="},{"pid":"26cd1945e592b6380ad64b6df9327f7c315ac1d4","tid":2435943,"uid":88133,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T16:25:31.000Z","msg":"新任香港中宣部部長"},{"pid":"1f80831c16544a8a7ad3aa5b6e6f5f699b1237ab","tid":2435943,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T16:37:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b4f3f492952ea7c7fd2c9867d25340810ce2fb1","tid":2435943,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"中宣部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d9685bcf2c91c8455ba896235abee2db851d90","tid":2435943,"uid":58880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T16:40:03.000Z","msg":"變做cctv算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d51a701c3db118b0216854d81df90e7f8